OL,3,CWhat is the Windrush Scandal and how
OL,4,Cdid it happen?
OL,6,FA report released on Wednesday
OL,7,Fexamined how laws aimed at reducing
OL,8,Fthe number of non-white people in
OL,9,FBritain affected the Windrush
OL,10,Fgeneration and its descendants.
OL,12,FThis issue reached a slow but
OL,13,Fclimactic conclusion in 2017, when it
OL,14,Fwas revealed government failures and
OL,15,Fthe Home Office's "hostile
OL,16,Fenvironment" policy led to threats of
OL,17,Fdeportation and detention for millions
OL,18,Fwho had legally migrated to the UK.
