OL,3,CWhat is the Windrush Scandal and how
OL,4,Cdid it happen?
OL,6,FIn April 2018 it emerged some people,
OL,7,Fwho migrated legally to the UK between
OL,8,Fthe late 1940s and early 1970s, were
OL,9,Fbeing threatened with detention and
OL,10,Fdeportation, despite having the right
OL,11,Fto live here.
OL,13,FThey were also denied access to their
OL,14,Fhousing, healthcare, bank accounts,
OL,15,Fand driving licences.
OL,17,FMany in the Windrush generation had no
OL,18,Frecord of their legal status.
